: Poly / Woven</li>\n<li>Base: High-density EVA form</li>\n<li>Thickness: 1.5mm ‚Äì 2.0mm</li>\n<li>Size: 23mm x 2200mm</li>\n<li>Accessory: End caps (black plastic) x 2</li>\n<li>Finishing tape (black) x 2</li>\n</ul>\n<p>BTP is now stocked by <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/collections/btp\" target=\"_blank\">Sim Works USA</a>.</p>\n<p>¬†</p>\n<hr />\n<p>¬†</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"858\" height=\"858\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/b1e02819-5bab-4b03-9eb4-83e27a35.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/b1e02819-5bab-4b03-9eb4-83e27a35.jpg?w=858&amp;quality=75 858w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/b1e02819-5bab-4b03-9eb4-83e27a35.jpg?resize=150,150&amp;quality=75 150w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/b1e02819-5bab-4b03-9eb4-83e27a35.jpg?resize=768,768&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/b1e02819-5bab-4b03-9eb4-83e27a35.jpg?resize=700,700&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1512\" height=\"2016\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/6c605bfa-1354-422a-8fd7-290e3663.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/6c605bfa-1354-422a-8fd7-290e3663.jpg?w=1512&amp;quality=75 1512w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/6c605bfa-1354-422a-8fd7-290e3663.jpg?resize=1024,1365&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/6c605bfa-1354-422a-8fd7-290e3663.jpg?resize=768,1024&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/6c605bfa-1354-422a-8fd7-290e3663.jpg?resize=1335,1780&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/6c605bfa-1354-422a-8fd7-290e3663.jpg?resize=700,933&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/10/6c605bfa-1354-422a-8fd7-290e3663.jpg?resize=1152,1536&amp;quality=75 1152w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.ther